# GitHub personal access token — optional, raises rate limit from
# 60 req/h (unauthenticated) to 5000 req/h (authenticated).
# Generate at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Scope needed: public_repo (read-only public data is sufficient).
#
# Two ways to use:
#   1) export GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_... && npm run fetch-github -- anthropics
#   2) put the line below in a .env file (gitignored), then on Node ≥ 20.6:
#        node --env-file=.env scripts/fetch-github.mjs anthropics
GITHUB_TOKEN=
